{"_id":"00b65e47a4dd7d76","name":"Vital Transfer","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"powerLevel":3,"discipline":"vital","useTheForce":15,"time":"Standard Action","range":"Touch","target":"One living creature","duration":"Instantaneous","effect":"<p>You channel the Force to heal injuries and restore vitality. The target recovers hit points based on your Use the Force check result.</p>","special":"<p>You cannot heal yourself with this power.</p>","descriptor":["Vital","Healing"],"dcChart":[{"dc":15,"effect":"2d6 healing","description":"Target heals 2d6 hit points"},{"dc":20,"effect":"4d6 healing","description":"Target heals 4d6 hit points"},{"dc":25,"effect":"6d6 healing + condition","description":"Target heals 6d6 hit points and removes one ongoing condition"},{"dc":30,"effect":"8d6 healing + all conditions","description":"Target heals 8d6 hit points and removes all ongoing conditions"}],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Saga Edition Core Rulebook","page":99,"tags":["force_power","healing","support","touch","standard_action","force_execution","skill_treat_injury","life_transfer"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"0419ecb55f011f81","name":"Farseeing","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"powerLevel":2,"discipline":"telepathic","useTheForce":20,"time":"1 minute","range":"Unlimited","target":"Special","duration":"Concentration","effect":"<p>You peer through the Force to see distant locations or events. You can observe a place you've been before or a person you know, regardless of distance.</p>","special":"<p>The GM may require additional checks for very distant or obscured visions.</p>","descriptor":["Mind-Affecting","Scrying"],"dcChart":[],"maintainable":true,"sourcebook":"Saga Edition Core Rulebook","page":95,"tags":["force_power","utility","divination","intel","perception","standard_action","ritual_like"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"0a422b939edfad56","name":"Force Lightning","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"powerLevel":4,"discipline":"dark-side","useTheForce":15,"time":"Standard Action","range":"6 squares","target":"One creature","duration":"Instantaneous","effect":"<p>You unleash devastating arcs of Force Lightning from your fingertips. The target takes lightning damage based on your Use the Force check result.</p>","special":"<p>This is a Dark Side power. Using it gains you a Dark Side Point.</p>","descriptor":["Dark Side","Force Lightning"],"dcChart":[{"dc":15,"effect":"2d6 lightning damage","description":"Target takes 2d6 lightning damage"},{"dc":20,"effect":"4d6 lightning damage","description":"Target takes 4d6 lightning damage"},{"dc":25,"effect":"6d6 lightning damage + stun","description":"Target takes 6d6 lightning damage and is stunned for 1 round"},{"dc":30,"effect":"8d6 lightning damage + stun 1d4","description":"Target takes 8d6 lightning damage and is stunned for 1d4 rounds"}],"maintainable":true,"sourcebook":"Saga Edition Core Rulebook","page":96,"tags":["force_power","offense_force","damage","dark_side","lightning","single_target","standard_action","force_execution"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"18e79be8d48946ba","name":"Force Cloak","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"powerLevel":2,"discipline":"telepathic","useTheForce":20,"time":"Standard Action","range":"Personal","target":"You","duration":"Concentration","effect":"<p>You bend light and perceptions around yourself, becoming invisible. You gain total concealment and a +10 bonus to Stealth checks.</p>","special":"<p>The invisibility ends if you attack or use another Force power.</p>","descriptor":["Mind-Affecting"],"dcChart":[],"maintainable":true,"sourcebook":"Saga Edition Core Rulebook","page":95,"tags":["force_power","stealth","concealment","invisibility","self_buff","standard_action","mobility"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"18f33f87a1ebee74","name":"Force Disarm","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"powerLevel":1,"discipline":"telekinetic","useTheForce":15,"time":"Standard Action","range":"6 squares","target":"One creature","duration":"Instantaneous","effect":"<p>You use telekinetic force to wrench a weapon or object from your target's grasp. Make a Use the Force check opposed by the target's Strength check or Will Defense (whichever is higher).</p>","special":"<p>On success, the target drops one held object of your choice.</p>","descriptor":["Telekinetic"],"dcChart":[],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Saga Edition Core Rulebook","page":96,"tags":["force_power","control","telekinetic","disarm","single_target","standard_action","weapon_denial"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"1ac1084ca8f07114","name":"Surge","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"powerLevel":1,"discipline":"vital","useTheForce":15,"time":"Swift Action","range":"Personal","target":"You","duration":"1 round","effect":"<p>You use the Force to push your body beyond normal limits. You gain an additional move action this turn.</p>","special":"<p>This extra move action can be used to move or perform other move-action tasks.</p>","descriptor":["Vital"],"dcChart":[],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Saga Edition Core Rulebook","page":99,"tags":["force_power","mobility","self_buff","swift_action","action_economy","extra_move","movement_boost"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"2466fc76adef817b","name":"Force Track","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"powerLevel":1,"discipline":"telepathic","useTheForce":15,"time":"1 minute","range":"Touch","target":"One creature","duration":"24 hours","effect":"<p>You place a Force 'mark' on your target, allowing you to track them through the Force. You always know the target's direction and approximate distance for the duration.</p>","special":"<p>The target can attempt a Will save (DC = your UTF check) to notice the mark.</p>","descriptor":["Mind-Affecting"],"dcChart":[],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Saga Edition Core Rulebook","page":97,"tags":["force_power","tracking","survival","intel","divination","standard_action"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"289013a32bd179ad","name":"Move Object","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"powerLevel":2,"discipline":"telekinetic","useTheForce":15,"time":"Standard Action","range":"12 squares","target":"One object or creature","duration":"Concentration","effect":"<p>You move objects or creatures through the air using telekinesis. The maximum size/weight you can move depends on your Use the Force check result.</p>","special":"<p>Unwilling creatures can make a Will save (DC = your UTF check) to resist being moved.</p>","descriptor":["Telekinetic"],"dcChart":[{"dc":15,"effect":"Medium (50 kg)","description":"Move objects up to Medium size or 50 kg"},{"dc":20,"effect":"Large (250 kg)","description":"Move objects up to Large size or 250 kg"},{"dc":25,"effect":"Huge (1 ton)","description":"Move objects up to Huge size or 1 metric ton"},{"dc":30,"effect":"Gargantuan (5 tons)","description":"Move objects up to Gargantuan size or 5 metric tons"},{"dc":35,"effect":"Colossal (20 tons)","description":"Move objects up to Colossal size or 20 metric tons (starfighter-sized)"}],"maintainable":true,"sourcebook":"Saga Edition Core Rulebook","page":98,"tags":["force_power","telekinetic","control","offense_force","forced_movement","utility","standard_action","single_target"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"390074b44aedfa2a","name":"Rebuke","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"powerLevel":2,"discipline":"telepathic","useTheForce":20,"time":"Standard Action","range":"6 squares","target":"One Force-sensitive creature","duration":"1 round","effect":"<p>You overwhelm a Force user with a powerful Force presence. If the target is Force-sensitive, they must make a Will save (DC = your UTF check) or be dazed for 1 round.</p>","special":"<p>This power only affects Force-sensitive creatures.</p>","descriptor":["Mind-Affecting"],"dcChart":[],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Saga Edition Core Rulebook","page":99,"tags":["force_power","anti_force","control","daze","single_target","standard_action","force_execution"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"462a6c23e00c4dfc","name":"Force Slam","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"powerLevel":2,"discipline":"telekinetic","useTheForce":20,"time":"Standard Action","range":"6 squares","target":"One creature or object","duration":"Instantaneous","effect":"<p>You use telekinetic force to violently slam your target against a surface. The target takes 4d6 damage and is knocked prone.</p>","special":"<p>The target must be within 6 squares of a solid surface (wall, floor, ceiling).</p>","descriptor":["Telekinetic"],"dcChart":[],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Saga Edition Core Rulebook","page":97,"tags":["force_power","offense_force","area","telekinetic","forced_movement","knockdown","standard_action"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"50be88fe6aa77d07","name":"Force Defense","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"powerLevel":1,"discipline":"telekinetic","useTheForce":15,"time":"Reaction","range":"Personal","target":"You","duration":"Instantaneous","effect":"<p>You use the Force to deflect an incoming attack. You gain a +5 Force bonus to your Reflex Defense against one attack.</p>","special":"<p>You must use this power before the attack roll is made.</p>","descriptor":["Telekinetic"],"dcChart":[],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Saga Edition Core Rulebook","page":96,"tags":["force_power","defense","anti_force","self_buff","reaction","utf_defense"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"64d987296e6bb054","name":"Force Scream","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"powerLevel":3,"discipline":"dark-side","useTheForce":20,"time":"Standard Action","range":"6-square cone","target":"All creatures in area","duration":"Instantaneous","effect":"<p>You unleash a Force-amplified scream that can shatter objects and stun enemies. All creatures in the area must make a Fortitude save (DC = your Use the Force check) or be stunned for 1 round.</p>","special":"<p>This is a Dark Side power.</p>","descriptor":["Dark Side","Sonic"],"dcChart":[],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Force Unleashed Campaign Guide","page":88,"tags":["force_power","offense_force","area","sonic","debuff","standard_action","dark_side"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"68353e70defb7efa","name":"Malacia","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"powerLevel":2,"discipline":"vital","useTheForce":20,"time":"Standard Action","range":"6 squares","target":"One living creature","duration":"1 round/level","effect":"<p>You disrupt your target's inner ear and equilibrium through the Force. The target must make a Fortitude save (DC = your UTF check) or become nauseated for the duration.</p>","special":"<p>This is a non-lethal Light Side power favored by Jedi.</p>","descriptor":["Vital","Mind-Affecting","Light Side"],"dcChart":[],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Saga Edition Core Rulebook","page":98,"tags":["force_power","control","condition_track","debuff","single_target","standard_action","telepathic"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"75838fe2c1165b3d","name":"Battle Meditation","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"powerLevel":2,"discipline":"telepathic","useTheForce":20,"time":"Standard Action","range":"12 squares","target":"Allies within range","duration":"Concentration (up to 1 minute)","effect":"<p>You bolster the morale and combat effectiveness of your allies through the Force. All allies within range gain a +2 morale bonus to attack rolls, damage rolls, and Will Defense.</p>","special":"<p>You must maintain concentration as a Swift Action each round to keep this power active.</p>","descriptor":["Mind-Affecting","Light Side"],"dcChart":[],"maintainable":true,"sourcebook":"Saga Edition Core Rulebook","page":94,"tags":["force_power","ally_support","leader","team_buff","standard_action","battlefield_control"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"7765b572c9f02bb0","name":"Force Weapon","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"powerLevel":1,"discipline":"telekinetic","useTheForce":15,"time":"Swift Action","range":"Touch","target":"One weapon","duration":"1 minute","effect":"<p>You imbue a weapon with the Force, allowing it to bypass damage reduction and strike incorporeal creatures normally.</p>","special":"<p>The weapon is treated as a Force weapon for the duration.</p>","descriptor":["Telekinetic"],"dcChart":[],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Saga Edition Core Rulebook","page":98,"tags":["force_power","offense_melee","weapon_buff","self_buff","swift_action","lightsaber","melee_buff"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"9a03352cce987282","name":"Drain Life","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"powerLevel":4,"discipline":"dark-side","useTheForce":15,"time":"Standard Action","range":"6 squares","target":"One living creature","duration":"Instantaneous","effect":"<p>You drain the life force from your target, transferring their vitality to yourself. The target takes damage and you heal an equal amount.</p>","special":"<p>This is a Dark Side power. Using it gains you a Dark Side Point.</p>","descriptor":["Dark Side","Life Drain"],"dcChart":[{"dc":15,"effect":"2d6 damage/heal","description":"Target takes 2d6 damage; you heal 2d6 hit points"},{"dc":20,"effect":"4d6 damage/heal","description":"Target takes 4d6 damage; you heal 4d6 hit points"},{"dc":25,"effect":"6d6 damage/heal + weakened","description":"Target takes 6d6 damage and is weakened; you heal 6d6 hit points"},{"dc":30,"effect":"8d6 damage/heal + exhausted","description":"Target takes 8d6 damage and is exhausted; you heal 8d6 hit points"}],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Saga Edition Core Rulebook","page":95,"tags":["force_power","offense_force","healing","dark_side","single_target","standard_action","life_drain"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"a214d4f56b4abe11","name":"Force Stun","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"powerLevel":2,"discipline":"telepathic","useTheForce":20,"time":"Standard Action","range":"6 squares","target":"One creature","duration":"1 round","effect":"<p>You use the Force to overwhelm your target's mind, stunning them. The target must make a Will save (DC = your UTF check) or be stunned for 1 round.</p>","special":"","descriptor":["Mind-Affecting"],"dcChart":[],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Saga Edition Core Rulebook","page":97,"tags":["force_power","control","stun","single_target","standard_action","telepathic"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"a4832d1e91a994b3","name":"Sever Force (Lesser)","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"powerLevel":3,"discipline":"dark-side","useTheForce":25,"time":"Standard Action","range":"6 squares","target":"One Force-sensitive creature","duration":"1 encounter","effect":"<p>You temporarily sever your target's connection to the Force. The target cannot use Force Powers or Force Talents for the duration.</p>","special":"<p>This is a Dark Side power. The target can make a Will save (DC = your UTF check) to resist.</p>","descriptor":["Dark Side","Force Drain"],"dcChart":[],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Saga Edition Core Rulebook","page":99,"tags":["force_power","anti_force","control","single_target","standard_action","force_denial"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"aef6dad242fd225b","name":"Force Storm","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"powerLevel":6,"discipline":"dark-side","useTheForce":30,"time":"Standard Action","range":"12 squares","target":"20-square radius","duration":"Concentration","effect":"<p>You create a massive Force storm of lightning and violent energy. All creatures in the area take 10d6 lightning damage each round (Reflex half, DC = your UTF check).</p>","special":"<p>This is a powerful Dark Side power. Using it gains you 2 Dark Side Points. Master-level power.</p>","descriptor":["Dark Side","Force Lightning","Area"],"dcChart":[{"dc":30,"effect":"10d6 to all in area","description":"All creatures in 20-square radius take 10d6 lightning damage (Reflex half)"},{"dc":35,"effect":"12d6 to all + stun","description":"All creatures take 12d6 damage (Reflex half) and are stunned 1 round (Fort negates)"},{"dc":40,"effect":"15d6 to all + disintegrate","description":"All creatures take 15d6 damage; those reduced to 0 HP are disintegrated"}],"maintainable":true,"sourcebook":"Saga Edition Core Rulebook","page":97,"tags":["force_power","offense_force","area","lightning","dark_side","standard_action","burst"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"b52769dd11b4e52c","name":"Sever Force","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"powerLevel":6,"discipline":"dark-side","useTheForce":30,"time":"1 minute","range":"Touch","target":"One Force-sensitive creature","duration":"Permanent","effect":"<p>You permanently sever a Force user's connection to the Force. The target loses all Force abilities permanently.</p>","special":"<p>This is an extremely powerful and cruel Dark Side power. Using it gains you 3 Dark Side Points. The target can make a Will save (DC = your UTF check) to resist. Master-level power.</p>","descriptor":["Dark Side","Force Drain"],"dcChart":[],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Saga Edition Core Rulebook","page":99,"tags":["force_power","anti_force","control","single_target","standard_action","force_denial","high_tier"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"b9a47b740e862b56","name":"Force Body","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"powerLevel":3,"discipline":"vital","useTheForce":25,"time":"Reaction","range":"Personal","target":"You","duration":"1 round","effect":"<p>You use the Force to push your body beyond its normal limits. You gain Damage Reduction 10 and a +4 bonus to Strength until the start of your next turn.</p>","special":"<p>You can activate this power as a Reaction when you take damage.</p>","descriptor":["Vital"],"dcChart":[],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Saga Edition Core Rulebook","page":95,"tags":["force_power","survivability","damage_mitigation","self_buff","swift_action","vital"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"be1ae263c498af3b","name":"Negate Energy","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"powerLevel":2,"discipline":"telekinetic","useTheForce":20,"time":"Reaction","range":"Personal or touch","target":"You or one creature","duration":"Instantaneous","effect":"<p>You use the Force to absorb or deflect energy damage. The target gains energy resistance 20 against one energy attack.</p>","special":"<p>This power can be used as a Reaction when you or an ally is targeted by an energy attack.</p>","descriptor":["Telekinetic"],"dcChart":[],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Saga Edition Core Rulebook","page":99,"tags":["force_power","defense","reaction","energy_defense","anti_blaster","survivability"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"c857835de924b420","name":"Force Sense","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"powerLevel":1,"discipline":"telepathic","useTheForce":15,"time":"Swift Action","range":"Personal","target":"You","duration":"1 round","effect":"<p>You open yourself to the Force, sensing danger and gaining heightened awareness. You cannot be surprised and gain a +5 bonus to Perception checks until the start of your next turn.</p>","special":"","descriptor":["Mind-Affecting"],"dcChart":[],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Saga Edition Core Rulebook","page":96,"tags":["force_power","perception","awareness","anti_stealth","utility","standard_action"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"d3d65e4805304da9","name":"Battlemind","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"powerLevel":1,"discipline":"telepathic","useTheForce":15,"time":"Swift Action","range":"Personal","target":"You","duration":"1 round","effect":"<p>You focus your mind through the Force, gaining tactical clarity. You gain a +2 insight bonus to Reflex Defense until the start of your next turn.</p>","special":"","descriptor":["Mind-Affecting"],"dcChart":[],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Saga Edition Core Rulebook","page":94,"tags":["force_power","self_buff","offense_melee","offense_ranged","accuracy","damage_buff","swift_action"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"d51bf85903366b6b","name":"Force Thrust","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"powerLevel":2,"discipline":"telekinetic","useTheForce":20,"time":"Standard Action","range":"6 squares","target":"One creature or object","duration":"Instantaneous","effect":"<p>You violently push your target away with telekinetic force. The target is pushed 6 squares away from you and knocked prone, taking 2d6 damage.</p>","special":"<p>If the target hits an obstacle during the push, they take an additional 1d6 damage per 2 squares not traveled.</p>","descriptor":["Telekinetic"],"dcChart":[],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Saga Edition Core Rulebook","page":97,"tags":["force_power","offense_force","telekinetic","forced_movement","single_target","standard_action"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"d5d13cf231f71929","name":"Drain Energy","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"powerLevel":3,"discipline":"dark-side","useTheForce":15,"time":"Standard Action","range":"6 squares","target":"One droid or electronic device","duration":"Instantaneous","effect":"<p>You drain the energy from technological devices through the Force. The target takes energy damage based on your Use the Force check result.</p>","special":"<p>This power only affects droids, vehicles, and electronic devices. This is a Dark Side power.</p>","descriptor":["Dark Side"],"dcChart":[{"dc":15,"effect":"2d6 energy damage","description":"Target takes 2d6 energy damage"},{"dc":20,"effect":"4d6 energy damage","description":"Target takes 4d6 energy damage"},{"dc":25,"effect":"6d6 energy damage + disabled","description":"Target takes 6d6 energy damage and is disabled for 1 round"},{"dc":30,"effect":"8d6 energy damage + shutdown","description":"Target takes 8d6 energy damage and shuts down for 1d4 rounds"}],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Saga Edition Core Rulebook","page":95,"tags":["force_power","anti_droid","anti_vehicle","offense_force","single_target","standard_action","ionic"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"dc331021badb59ed","name":"Inspire","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"powerLevel":1,"discipline":"telepathic","useTheForce":15,"time":"Swift Action","range":"6 squares","target":"One ally","duration":"1 round","effect":"<p>You inspire an ally through the Force, granting them confidence and clarity. The target gains a +2 morale bonus to their next attack roll or skill check.</p>","special":"","descriptor":["Mind-Affecting"],"dcChart":[],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Saga Edition Core Rulebook","page":98,"tags":["force_power","ally_support","team_buff","morale","standard_action","leader"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"e2cfcd6f4097fa30","name":"Force Strike","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"powerLevel":1,"discipline":"telekinetic","useTheForce":15,"time":"Standard Action","range":"6 squares","target":"One creature","duration":"Instantaneous","effect":"<p>You strike your target with a telekinetic blow. The target takes 2d6 Force damage and must make a Fortitude save (DC = your UTF check) or be knocked prone.</p>","special":"","descriptor":["Telekinetic"],"dcChart":[],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Saga Edition Core Rulebook","page":97,"tags":["force_power","offense_force","single_target","telekinetic","standard_action","damage"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"e6649f366d6c5737","name":"Mind Trick","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"powerLevel":1,"discipline":"telepathic","useTheForce":15,"time":"Standard Action","range":"6 squares","target":"One creature","duration":"1 minute or until completed","effect":"<p>You influence a weak mind to believe what you tell them or follow a simple suggestion. The target must make a Will save (DC = your UTF check) or be affected.</p>","special":"<p>The suggestion must be reasonable and the target must be able to understand you.</p>","descriptor":["Mind-Affecting"],"dcChart":[],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Saga Edition Core Rulebook","page":98,"tags":["force_power","social","control","mind_affecting","single_target","standard_action","deception"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"f177dc6d65f76de9","name":"Battle Strike","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"powerLevel":1,"discipline":"telekinetic","useTheForce":15,"time":"Swift Action","range":"Personal","target":"You","duration":"1 round","effect":"<p>You channel the Force to enhance your next melee attack. Your next melee attack this round gains a +1d6 bonus to damage.</p>","special":"<p>This bonus damage is Force damage and bypasses Damage Reduction.</p>","descriptor":["Telekinetic"],"dcChart":[],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Saga Edition Core Rulebook","page":94,"tags":["force_power","offense_melee","self_buff","damage_buff","swift_action","melee_buff"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fp_ballistakinesis","name":"Ballistakinesis","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","system":{"powerLevel":3,"discipline":"telekinetic","useTheForce":15,"time":"Standard Action","range":"12 squares","target":"2x2 area","duration":"Instantaneous","effect":"You use The Force to spray an area with dangerous debris.","special":"Spend a Force Point to deal half damage to targets that fail their Reflex Defense.","descriptor":["Telekinetic"],"dcChart":[{"dc":15,"effect":"3d8 damage","description":"Targets take 3d8 damage and suffer -2 to attack rolls until the start of your next turn."}],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Legacy Era Campaign Guide","page":null,"tags":["force_power","offense_ranged","control","weapon_buff","standard_action","blaster_synergy"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fp_blind","name":"Blind","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/blind.svg","system":{"powerLevel":1,"discipline":"telekinetic","useTheForce":15,"time":"Swift Action","range":"12 squares","target":"One creature","duration":"Until the start of your next turn","effect":"You hurl dirt, dust, and debris at your foe, affecting its sight.","special":"Creatures that do not rely on sight are immune. Spend a Force Point to activate as a Free Action.","descriptor":["Telekinetic"],"dcChart":[{"dc":15,"effect":"Flat-footed","description":"Target becomes Flat-Footed and all other creatures gain Concealment from the target."}],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Jedi Academy Training Manual","page":null,"tags":["force_power","control","debuff","single_target","standard_action","vision_denial"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fp_combustion","name":"Combustion","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/fire.svg","system":{"powerLevel":3,"discipline":"pyrokinesis","useTheForce":15,"time":"Standard Action","range":"12 squares","target":"2x2 area","duration":"Instantaneous","effect":"You use The Force to agitate particles in the air to create a pyrokinetic spray of sparks.","special":"Spend a Force Point to move one affected target -1 step on the Condition Track.","descriptor":["Fire"],"dcChart":[{"dc":15,"effect":"4d6 fire","description":"Targets take 4d6 fire damage and catch on fire."}],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Legacy Era Campaign Guide","page":null,"tags":["force_power","offense_force","damage","fire","single_target","standard_action"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fp_convection","name":"Convection","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/fire.svg","system":{"powerLevel":2,"discipline":"pyrokinesis","useTheForce":15,"time":"Swift Action","range":"Self","target":"Self","duration":"Until the start of your next turn","effect":"You alter your body chemistry, causing your skin to burn with incredible heat.","special":"You can maintain Convection with a Swift Action each round. If you take damage while maintaining it you must succeed on a Use the Force check (DC 15 + damage taken). Spend a Force Point to deal the bonus damage to creatures striking you with unarmed attacks or grapples.","descriptor":["Fire"],"dcChart":[{"dc":15,"effect":"+1d6 fire damage","description":"Your unarmed attacks deal +1d6 fire damage and targets catch on fire."},{"dc":20,"effect":"+2d6 fire damage","description":"Your unarmed attacks deal +2d6 fire damage and targets catch on fire."},{"dc":25,"effect":"+3d6 fire damage","description":"Your unarmed attacks deal +3d6 fire damage and targets catch on fire."},{"dc":30,"effect":"+4d6 fire damage","description":"Your unarmed attacks deal +4d6 fire damage and targets catch on fire."}],"maintainable":true,"sourcebook":"Jedi Academy Training Manual","page":null,"tags":["force_power","offense_force","area","fire","hazard","standard_action"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fp_corruption","name":"Corruption","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/skull.svg","system":{"powerLevel":4,"discipline":"dark","useTheForce":15,"time":"Standard Action","range":"12 squares","target":"One creature","duration":"Multiple rounds","effect":"You use The Force to send a bolt of pure Dark Side vilness into an enemy.","special":"Spend a Force Point when you successfully damage a target to have all creatures adjacent to the target take half damage if the Use the Force check also exceeds their Fortitude Defense.","descriptor":["Dark Side"],"dcChart":[{"dc":15,"effect":"2d6 damage","description":"Target takes 2d6 Force damage and half that again at the start of its turn."},{"dc":20,"effect":"3d6 damage","description":"Target takes 3d6 Force damage and half again next round."},{"dc":25,"effect":"4d6 damage","description":"Target takes 4d6 Force damage and half again next round."},{"dc":30,"effect":"5d6 damage","description":"Target takes 5d6 Force damage and half again next round."}],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Force Unleashed Campaign Guide","page":null,"tags":["force_power","offense_force","dark_side","ongoing_damage","debuff","single_target","standard_action"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fp_crucitorn","name":"Crucitorn","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/shield.svg","system":{"powerLevel":2,"discipline":"control","useTheForce":15,"time":"Reaction","range":"Self","target":"Self","duration":"Instantaneous","effect":"You ignore the debilitating effects of pain and focus through trauma.","special":"Spend a Force Point to increase the bonus to Damage Threshold by an additional +5.","descriptor":["Control"],"dcChart":[{"dc":15,"effect":"+5 Damage Threshold","description":"Gain +5 Force bonus to Damage Threshold against the triggering attack."},{"dc":20,"effect":"+10 Damage Threshold","description":"Gain +10 Force bonus to Damage Threshold against the triggering attack."},{"dc":25,"effect":"+15 Damage Threshold","description":"Gain +15 Force bonus to Damage Threshold against the triggering attack."},{"dc":30,"effect":"+20 Damage Threshold","description":"Gain +20 Force bonus to Damage Threshold against the triggering attack."}],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Jedi Academy Training Manual","page":null,"tags":["force_power","offense_force","dark_side","pain","control","single_target","standard_action"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fp_darkrage","name":"Dark Rage","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/skull.svg","system":{"powerLevel":1,"discipline":"dark","useTheForce":15,"time":"Swift Action","range":"Self","target":"Self","duration":"Until end of your turn","effect":"You become enraged as the Dark Side flows through you.","special":"While consumed by Rage, you cannot use Skills or perform tasks that require patience or concentration. You can spend a Force Point to extend the duration of your Dark Rage until the end of the encounter.","descriptor":["Dark Side"],"dcChart":[{"dc":15,"effect":"+2 rage bonus","description":"+2 bonus to melee attack and damage rolls."},{"dc":20,"effect":"+4 rage bonus","description":"+4 bonus to melee attack and damage rolls."},{"dc":25,"effect":"+6 rage bonus","description":"+6 bonus to melee attack and damage rolls."}],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Jedi Academy Training Manual","page":null,"tags":["force_power","offense_melee","self_buff","dark_side","damage_buff","swift_action","risk_reward"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fp_darktransfer","name":"Dark Transfer","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/heal.svg","system":{"powerLevel":3,"discipline":"dark","useTheForce":15,"time":"Standard Action","range":"Touch","target":"One living creature","duration":"Instantaneous","effect":"You use The Dark Side of The Force to restore vitality to a living ally.","special":"Each use moves you -1 persistent step down the Condition Track unless you spend a Force Point.","descriptor":["Dark Side","Healing"],"dcChart":[{"dc":15,"effect":"Heal level HP","description":"Target heals HP equal to your character level."},{"dc":20,"effect":"Heal 2x level","description":"Target heals twice your character level."},{"dc":25,"effect":"Heal 3x level","description":"Target heals three times your character level."},{"dc":30,"effect":"Heal 4x level","description":"Target heals four times your character level."}],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Legacy Era Campaign Guide","page":null,"tags":["force_power","healing","dark_side","support","touch","standard_action","resource_cost"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fp_detonate","name":"Detonate","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","system":{"powerLevel":3,"discipline":"telekinetic","useTheForce":20,"time":"Standard Action","range":"12 squares","target":"One unattended object","duration":"Instantaneous","effect":"You can perceive points of weakness within an object and use The Force to telekinetically press on one of those points, shattering the object.","special":"You may spend a Force Point when you activate this Force Power.","descriptor":["Telekinetic"],"dcChart":[{"dc":20,"effect":"4d6 damage","description":"The object takes 4d6 damage."},{"dc":25,"effect":"6d6 damage","description":"The object takes 6d6 damage."},{"dc":30,"effect":"8d6 damage","description":"The object takes 8d6 damage."},{"dc":35,"effect":"10d6 damage","description":"The object takes 10d6 damage."}],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Legacy Era Campaign Guide","page":null,"tags":["force_power","offense_force","area","explosive","standard_action","object_interaction"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fp_energyresistance","name":"Energy Resistance","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/shield.svg","system":{"powerLevel":1,"discipline":"control","useTheForce":20,"time":"Standard Action","range":"Self","target":"Self","duration":"Until beginning of next turn","effect":"You use The Force to protect you from damage caused by energy, sonic, fire, cold, and electrical sources.","special":"You can spend a Force Point to use this Force Power as a Swift Action, rather than a Standard Action. You can maintain Energy Resistance from round to round, extending the normal duration. Maintaining the Energy Resistance Force Power is a Swift Action. If you take damage while maintaining Energy Resistance, you must succeed on a Use the Force check (DC = 15 + damage taken) to continue maintaining the Energy Resistance.","descriptor":["Control"],"dcChart":[{"dc":20,"effect":"DR 5","description":"Gain Damage Reduction 5 vs energy damage."},{"dc":25,"effect":"DR 10","description":"Gain Damage Reduction 10 vs energy damage."},{"dc":30,"effect":"DR 15","description":"Gain Damage Reduction 15 vs energy damage."},{"dc":35,"effect":"DR 20","description":"Gain Damage Reduction 20 vs energy damage."}],"maintainable":true,"sourcebook":"Knights of the Old Republic Campaign Guide","page":null,"tags":["force_power","defense","energy_defense","ally_support","self_buff","standard_action"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fp_enlighten","name":"Enlighten","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/light.svg","system":{"powerLevel":2,"discipline":"telepathic","useTheForce":15,"time":"Reaction or Swift Action","range":"12 squares","target":"One ally","duration":"Until start of your next turn","effect":"You reach out to an ally telepathically, sharing visions of the near future to give the ally an edge or to protect the ally from harm.","special":"You may spend a Force Point when you activate this Force Power to prolong the effect until the end of your next turn.","descriptor":["Light Side","Mind-Affecting"],"dcChart":[{"dc":15,"effect":"Insight replacement","description":"Target may replace one attack roll, skill check, or Defense with your Use the Force result."}],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Legacy Era Campaign Guide","page":null,"tags":["force_power","utility","knowledge","intel","perception","standard_action","investigation"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fp_fear","name":"Fear","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/skull.svg","system":{"powerLevel":1,"discipline":"dark","useTheForce":15,"time":"Swift Action","range":"12 squares","target":"One creature","duration":"1 round","effect":"You summon The Dark Side to instill fear in your enemies.","special":"When you successfully use this Force Power on an opponent, you can spend a Force Point to impose a -2 penalty on all of the target's Defenses until the beginning of your next turn.","descriptor":["Dark Side","Mind-Affecting"],"dcChart":[{"dc":15,"effect":"Standard only","description":"Target can take only one Standard Action."},{"dc":20,"effect":"Move only","description":"Target can take only one Move Action."},{"dc":25,"effect":"Swift only","description":"Target can take only one Swift Action."},{"dc":30,"effect":"No actions","description":"Target cannot take actions on its next turn."}],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Knights of the Old Republic Campaign Guide","page":null,"tags":["force_power","control","mind_affecting","debuff","area","standard_action","dark_side"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fp_foldspace","name":"Fold Space","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/teleport.svg","system":{"powerLevel":5,"discipline":"telekinetic","useTheForce":20,"time":"Full-Round Action","range":"6 squares","target":"One held or unattended object or Vehicle","duration":"Instantaneous","effect":"You can use The Force to bend space, transporting an object almost instantaneously from one place to another.","special":"If the object you are transporting contains other objects or creatures (such as a Starship), everything contained within the object is transported as well. You can spend a Force Point to increase the maximum size of the object you can move by two categories, up to Colossal (Cruiser) in size, or double the distance the object is transported.","descriptor":["Telekinetic"],"dcChart":[{"dc":20,"effect":"Medium, 6 sq","description":"You can move a Medium or smaller object up to 6 squares."},{"dc":25,"effect":"Large, 12 sq","description":"You can move a Large or smaller object up to 12 squares."},{"dc":30,"effect":"Huge, 18 sq","description":"You can move a Huge or smaller object up to 18 squares."},{"dc":35,"effect":"Gargantuan, 24 sq","description":"You can move a Gargantuan or smaller object up to 24 squares."},{"dc":40,"effect":"Colossal, 30 sq","description":"You can move a Colossal or smaller object up to 30 squares."}],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Jedi Academy Training Manual","page":null,"tags":["force_power","mobility","teleport","utility","standard_action","positioning"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fp_forceblast","name":"Force Blast","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","system":{"powerLevel":4,"discipline":"telekinetic","useTheForce":15,"time":"Standard Action","range":"12 squares","target":"One creature","duration":"Instantaneous","effect":"You use The Force to create a ball of compressed air and debris that you can hurl at enemy targets.","special":"You can spend a Force Point to add one-half your Heroic Level as a damage bonus on a Force Blast.","descriptor":["Telekinetic"],"dcChart":[{"dc":15,"effect":"2d6 damage","description":"The Force Blast deals 2d6 points of damage to the target."},{"dc":20,"effect":"3d6 damage","description":"The Force Blast deals 3d6 points of damage to the target."},{"dc":25,"effect":"4d6 damage","description":"The Force Blast deals 4d6 points of damage to the target."},{"dc":30,"effect":"5d6 damage","description":"The Force Blast deals 5d6 points of damage to the target."}],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Force Unleashed Campaign Guide","page":null,"tags":["force_power","offense_force","area","telekinetic","push","standard_action"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fp_forcelight","name":"Force Light","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/light.svg","system":{"powerLevel":4,"discipline":"light","useTheForce":20,"time":"Standard Action","range":"6 squares","target":"All creatures with Dark Side Score","duration":"Until the start of your next turn","effect":"You can draw The Force into yourself, turning you into a beacon of light that purges the taint of The Dark Side.","special":"You can spend a Force Point to increase the damage dealt by an additional +1d6 points of Force damage. You can maintain Force Light from round to round, extending the normal duration. Maintaining the Force Light Force Power is a Standard Action, and you must make a new Use the Force check each round. If you take damage while maintaining Force Light, you must succeed on a Use the Force check (DC = 15 + damage taken) to continue maintaining the Force Light.","descriptor":["Light Side"],"dcChart":[{"dc":20,"effect":"1d6 damage","description":"Any creature with a Dark Side Score of 1+, that begins its turn within 6 squares of you, automatically takes 1d6 points of Force damage, and takes a -1 penalty on attack rolls."},{"dc":25,"effect":"2d6 damage","description":"Any creature with a Dark Side Score of 1+, that begins its turn within 6 squares of you, automatically takes 2d6 points of Force damage, and takes a -1 penalty on attack rolls."},{"dc":30,"effect":"3d6 damage","description":"Any creature with a Dark Side Score of 1+, that begins its turn within 6 squares of you, automatically takes 3d6 points of Force damage, and takes a -1 penalty on attack rolls."},{"dc":35,"effect":"4d6 damage","description":"Any creature with a Dark Side Score of 1+, that begins its turn within 6 squares of you, automatically takes 4d6 points of Force damage, and takes a -1 penalty on attack rolls."}],"maintainable":true,"sourcebook":"Jedi Academy Training Manual","page":null,"tags":["force_power","anti_dark_side","support","area","standard_action","purification"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fp_forceshield","name":"Force Shield","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/shield.svg","system":{"powerLevel":1,"discipline":"telekinetic","useTheForce":15,"time":"Reaction","range":"Self","target":"Self","duration":"Until beginning of next turn","effect":"You use The Force to create a bubble of telekinetic energy around yourself, protecting you from harm.","special":"You can spend a Force Point when you activate this Force Power to increase the Force Shield's Shield Rating by 5. You can maintain Force Shield from round to round, extending the normal duration. Maintaining the Force Shield Force Power is a Standard Action. If the Force Shield's Shield Rating is ever reduced to 0, the Force Power's effect ends.","descriptor":["Telekinetic"],"dcChart":[{"dc":15,"effect":"SR 5","description":"You gain a Shield Rating (SR) of 5 until the beginning of your next turn."},{"dc":20,"effect":"SR 10","description":"You gain a Shield Rating (SR) of 10 until the beginning of your next turn."},{"dc":25,"effect":"SR 15","description":"You gain a Shield Rating (SR) of 15 until the beginning of your next turn."},{"dc":30,"effect":"SR 20","description":"You gain a Shield Rating (SR) of 20 until the beginning of your next turn."}],"maintainable":true,"sourcebook":"Force Unleashed Campaign Guide","page":null,"tags":["force_power","defense","shielding","self_buff","standard_action","survivability"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fp_forcewhirlwind","name":"Force Whirlwind","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/vortex.svg","system":{"powerLevel":4,"discipline":"telekinetic","useTheForce":20,"time":"Standard Action","range":"12 squares","target":"One creature or Droid","duration":"Until beginning of next turn","effect":"You call upon The Force to surround an enemy in a swirling vortex of Force energy. The whirlwind lifts them about half a meter off the ground, spinning them in the air and buffeting them with Force energy.","special":"You can spend a Force Point to increase the penalty to the target's attack rolls and Skill Checks while inside the whirlwind from a -5 penalty to a -10 penalty. You can maintain Force Whirlwind from round to round, extending the normal duration. Maintaining the Force Whirlwind Force Power is a Move Action, and you must make a new Use the Force check each round. If you take damage while maintaining Force Whirlwind, you must succeed on a Use the Force check (DC = 15 + damage taken) to continue maintaining the Force Whirlwind.","descriptor":["Telekinetic"],"dcChart":[{"dc":15,"effect":"1d6 damage, -5 penalty","description":"Target takes 1d6 Force damage and is immobilized with -5 penalty to attacks/checks."},{"dc":20,"effect":"2d6 damage, -5 penalty","description":"Target takes 2d6 Force damage and is immobilized with -5 penalty to attacks/checks."},{"dc":25,"effect":"3d6 damage, -5 penalty","description":"Target takes 3d6 Force damage and is immobilized with -5 penalty to attacks/checks."},{"dc":30,"effect":"4d6 damage, -5 penalty","description":"Target takes 4d6 Force damage and is immobilized with -5 penalty to attacks/checks."}],"maintainable":true,"sourcebook":"Knights of the Old Republic Campaign Guide","page":null,"tags":["force_power","control","forced_movement","lift","single_target","standard_action"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fp_hatred","name":"Hatred","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/skull.svg","system":{"powerLevel":2,"discipline":"dark","useTheForce":20,"time":"Standard Action","range":"6 squares","target":"All creatures within 6 squares","duration":"Until end of your next turn","effect":"You give yourself over to The Dark Side, letting your hate radiate out from your body in palpable waves.","special":"You can spend a Force Point to increase the damage dealt by an additional +1d6 points of Force damage. You can maintain Hatred from round to round, extending the normal duration. Maintaining the Hatred Force Power is a Swift Action, and you must make a new Use the Force check each round. If you take damage while maintaining Hatred, you must succeed on a Use the Force check (DC = 15 + damage taken) to continue maintaining the Hatred.","descriptor":["Dark Side"],"dcChart":[{"dc":15,"effect":"1d6 damage, -1 Defense","description":"Any creature that starts its turn within 6 squares of you takes 1d6 Force damage and -1 penalty to all Defenses."},{"dc":20,"effect":"2d6 damage, -1 Defense","description":"Any creature that starts its turn within 6 squares of you takes 2d6 Force damage and -1 penalty to all Defenses."},{"dc":25,"effect":"3d6 damage, -1 Defense","description":"Any creature that starts its turn within 6 squares of you takes 3d6 Force damage and -1 penalty to all Defenses."},{"dc":30,"effect":"4d6 damage, -1 Defense","description":"Any creature that starts its turn within 6 squares of you takes 4d6 Force damage and -1 penalty to all Defenses."}],"maintainable":true,"sourcebook":"Jedi Academy Training Manual","page":null,"tags":["force_power","dark_side","self_buff","force_point_recovery","swift_action","resource_recovery"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fp_inertia","name":"Inertia","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/flight.svg","system":{"powerLevel":2,"discipline":"control","useTheForce":15,"time":"Move Action","range":"Self","target":"Self","duration":"Instantaneous","effect":"You can use The Force to shift your body's inertia, allowing you to perform impossible stunts.","special":"You can spend a Force Point to increase the Speed you move along the wall by an additional +2 squares.","descriptor":["Control"],"dcChart":[{"dc":15,"effect":"Half speed, walls","description":"You can move up to half your Speed along a wall, ignoring gravity."},{"dc":20,"effect":"Full speed, walls","description":"You can move up to your full Speed along a wall, ignoring gravity."},{"dc":25,"effect":"Speed +2, walls","description":"You can move up to your full Speed, +2 additional squares, along a wall, ignoring gravity."},{"dc":30,"effect":"Speed +4, walls","description":"You can move up to your full Speed, +4 additional squares, along a wall, ignoring gravity."}],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Jedi Academy Training Manual","page":null,"tags":["force_power","defense","damage_mitigation","fall_protection","self_buff","reaction"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fp_intercept","name":"Intercept","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/shield.svg","system":{"powerLevel":3,"discipline":"telekinetic","useTheForce":15,"time":"Reaction","range":"Self","target":"One incoming ranged attack","duration":"Instantaneous","effect":"You use The Force to telekinetically hurl a small object in the path of an incoming projectile, preventing it from striking you.","special":"You can use this Force Power to negate an object being used as a projectile weapon with the Move Light Object application of the Use the Force skill, or the Move Object Force Power. You can spend a Force Point to use this Force Power to intercept some of the barrage of shots from a ranged weapon set on Autofire.","descriptor":["Telekinetic"],"dcChart":[{"dc":15,"effect":"Negate attack","description":"If your Use the Force check equals or exceeds the attack roll result, you negate the attack against you."}],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Jedi Academy Training Manual","page":null,"tags":["force_power","defense","reaction","ranged_defense","projectile_intercept","telekinetic"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fp_ionize","name":"Ionize","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/lightning.svg","system":{"powerLevel":2,"discipline":"telekinetic","useTheForce":20,"time":"Standard Action","range":"6 squares","target":"One target","duration":"Instantaneous","effect":"You call upon The Force to overload electrical systems and Droids, damaging or even destroying the unit.","special":"You can spend a Force Point to increase the Ion damage dealt by this Force Power by an additional 2d6 points of Ion damage.","descriptor":["Telekinetic"],"dcChart":[{"dc":20,"effect":"4d6 ion","description":"The target takes 4d6 points of Ion damage."},{"dc":25,"effect":"5d6 ion","description":"The target takes 5d6 points of Ion damage."},{"dc":30,"effect":"6d6 ion","description":"The target takes 6d6 points of Ion damage."}],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Knights of the Old Republic Campaign Guide","page":null,"tags":["force_power","anti_droid","anti_vehicle","ionic","single_target","standard_action","control"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fp_kineticcombat","name":"Kinetic Combat","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/sword.svg","system":{"powerLevel":4,"discipline":"telekinetic","useTheForce":20,"time":"Standard Action","range":"12 squares","target":"One one-handed Melee Weapon","duration":"Until beginning of next turn","effect":"You use The Force to manipulate your chosen Weapon, allowing it to operate independent of your grasp.","special":"You can spend a Force Point to gain a +1 bonus on attack rolls with a weapon wielded using Kinetic Combat. You can maintain Kinetic Combat from round to round, extending the normal duration. Maintaining the Kinetic Combat Force Power is a Swift Action, and as a Standard Action each round you can direct the weapon to move up to 6 squares, and make a single attack against a target adjacent to the weapon.","descriptor":["Telekinetic"],"dcChart":[{"dc":20,"effect":"Wield remotely","description":"You can telekinetically move a one-handed melee weapon up to 12 squares away and make an attack with it using Charisma modifier."}],"maintainable":true,"sourcebook":"Knights of the Old Republic Campaign Guide","page":null,"tags":["force_power","offense_melee","weapon_buff","telekinetic","self_buff","swift_action","lightsaber_adjacent"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fp_levitate","name":"Levitate","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/flight.svg","system":{"powerLevel":2,"discipline":"telekinetic","useTheForce":15,"time":"Move Action","range":"Self","target":"Self","duration":"Until beginning of next turn","effect":"You can float up or down without anything or anyone to assist you.","special":"You can spend a Force Point as a Reaction to activate Levitate when falling. You can reduce your fall distance by a number of squares equal to the Fly Speed provided by this Force Power. You can maintain Levitate from round to round, extending the normal duration. Maintaining the Levitate Force Power is a Move Action, and whenever you maintain this Force Power you can move vertically up to your Fly Speed.","descriptor":["Telekinetic"],"dcChart":[{"dc":15,"effect":"Fly 2 sq vertical","description":"You gain a Fly Speed of 2 squares but can only move vertically."},{"dc":20,"effect":"Fly 4 sq vertical","description":"You gain a Fly Speed of 4 squares but can only move vertically."},{"dc":25,"effect":"Fly 6 sq vertical","description":"You gain a Fly Speed of 6 squares but can only move vertically."}],"maintainable":true,"sourcebook":"Clone Wars Campaign Guide","page":null,"tags":["force_power","mobility","vertical_movement","utility","standard_action"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fp_lightningburst","name":"Lightning Burst","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/lightning.svg","system":{"powerLevel":4,"discipline":"dark","useTheForce":20,"time":"Standard Action","range":"Adjacent","target":"All enemies adjacent to you","duration":"Instantaneous","effect":"You call upon The Dark Side to cause lightning to arc out from your body, striking adjacent enemies.","special":"You may spend a Force Point when you activate this Force Power to increase the damage dealt by +2d6. You can maintain the Lightning Burst Force Power as a Standard Action, provided you haven't moved since activating the Force Power.","descriptor":["Dark Side"],"dcChart":[{"dc":20,"effect":"3d6 damage, -1 Condition","description":"Target takes 3d6 Force damage and moves -1 step along the Condition Track."}],"maintainable":true,"sourcebook":"Legacy Era Campaign Guide","page":null,"tags":["force_power","offense_force","area","lightning","standard_action","dark_side"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fp_memorywalk","name":"Memory Walk","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/skull.svg","system":{"powerLevel":3,"discipline":"dark","useTheForce":20,"time":"Standard Action","range":"6 squares","target":"One creature with Intelligence 3+","duration":"Until beginning of next turn","effect":"You torment an enemy by causing them to relive their most horrible memories.","special":"You can spend a Force Point to increase the damage dealt by an additional +2d6 points of Force damage. You can maintain Memory Walk from round to round, extending the normal duration. Maintaining the Memory Walk Force Power is a Standard Action, and you must make a new Use the Force check each round.","descriptor":["Dark Side","Mind-Affecting"],"dcChart":[{"dc":20,"effect":"2d6 damage, -Swift","description":"Target takes 2d6 Force damage and loses its Swift Action on its next turn."},{"dc":25,"effect":"2d6 damage, -Move","description":"Target takes 2d6 Force damage and loses its Move Action on its next turn."},{"dc":30,"effect":"2d6 damage, -Standard","description":"Target takes 2d6 Force damage and loses its Standard Action on its next turn."},{"dc":35,"effect":"2d6 damage, -Standard/-Swift","description":"Target takes 2d6 Force damage and loses both Standard and Swift Actions on its next turn."}],"maintainable":true,"sourcebook":"Jedi Academy Training Manual","page":null,"tags":["force_power","intel","investigation","telepathic","mind_probe","standard_action","single_target"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fp_mindshard","name":"Mind Shard","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/skull.svg","system":{"powerLevel":2,"discipline":"telepathic","useTheForce":15,"time":"Standard Action","range":"12 squares","target":"One creature","duration":"Instantaneous","effect":"You use The Force to splinter the mind of an opponent, wracking it with pain.","special":"You can spend a Force Point to increase the damage dealt by an additional +2d8 points of Force damage.","descriptor":["Mind-Affecting"],"dcChart":[{"dc":15,"effect":"2d8 damage, -1 Condition","description":"Target takes 2d8 Force damage and moves -1 step down the Condition Track."},{"dc":20,"effect":"3d8 damage, -1 Condition","description":"Target takes 3d8 Force damage and moves -1 step down the Condition Track."},{"dc":25,"effect":"4d8 damage, -1 Condition","description":"Target takes 4d8 Force damage and moves -1 step down the Condition Track."},{"dc":30,"effect":"5d8 damage, -1 Condition","description":"Target takes 5d8 Force damage and moves -1 step down the Condition Track."}],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Jedi Academy Training Manual","page":null,"tags":["force_power","offense_force","telepathic","single_target","debuff","standard_action"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fp_morichro","name":"Morichro","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/sleep.svg","system":{"powerLevel":4,"discipline":"control","useTheForce":20,"time":"Standard Action","range":"Touch","target":"One living creature you have Grabbed","duration":"Until beginning of next turn","effect":"You slow the vital functions of a target, causing them to slip into a deep sleep or even die.","special":"Each round you maintain this Force Power, if your Use the Force check exceeds the target's Fortitude Defense, the target moves another step down the Condition Track. You can maintain Morichro from round to round, extending the normal duration. Maintaining the Morichro Force Power is a Standard Action, and you must make a new Use the Force check each round.","descriptor":["Control"],"dcChart":[{"dc":20,"effect":"Move -1 Condition","description":"Target moves -1 step down the Condition Track."}],"maintainable":true,"sourcebook":"Clone Wars Campaign Guide","page":null,"tags":["force_power","control","single_target","save_or_sleep","dark_side","standard_action"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fp_obscure","name":"Obscure","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/blind.svg","system":{"powerLevel":2,"discipline":"telepathic","useTheForce":15,"time":"Reaction","range":"12 squares","target":"One target that just made an attack","duration":"Instantaneous","effect":"You use The Force to cloud an enemy's mind, making it harder for the enemy to see its target.","special":"You may spend a Force Point when you activate this Force Power to apply the penalty to all of the target's attack rolls made until the start of its next turn.","descriptor":["Mind-Affecting"],"dcChart":[{"dc":15,"effect":"-5 penalty","description":"Target takes a -5 penalty on the attack roll."}],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Legacy Era Campaign Guide","page":null,"tags":["force_power","stealth","concealment","ally_support","area","standard_action"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fp_phase","name":"Phase","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/teleport.svg","system":{"powerLevel":5,"discipline":"telekinetic","useTheForce":25,"time":"Move Action","range":"Self","target":"Self","duration":"Until beginning of next turn","effect":"You can pass through solid objects, such as walls and doors.","special":"You can spend a Force Point to increase your Phasing Speed by 2 squares. You can maintain Phase from round to round, extending the normal duration. Maintaining the Phase Force Power is a Move Action, and whenever you maintain this Force Power you can move up to your Phasing Speed.","descriptor":["Telekinetic"],"dcChart":[{"dc":25,"effect":"Phase 2 sq","description":"You gain a Phasing Speed of 2 squares."},{"dc":30,"effect":"Phase 4 sq","description":"You gain a Phasing Speed of 4 squares."},{"dc":35,"effect":"Phase 6 sq","description":"You gain a Phasing Speed of 6 squares."},{"dc":40,"effect":"Phase 8 sq","description":"You gain a Phasing Speed of 8 squares."}],"maintainable":true,"sourcebook":"Clone Wars Campaign Guide","page":null,"tags":["force_power","mobility","defense","escape","self_buff","standard_action","intangibility"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fp_plantsurge","name":"Plant Surge","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/plant.svg","system":{"powerLevel":2,"discipline":"control","useTheForce":15,"time":"Standard Action","range":"12 squares","target":"One creature","duration":"Until beginning of next turn","effect":"You reach out with The Force to entreat the aid of plants, causing them to lash out at your opponents.","special":"There must be one or more plants adjacent to the target, or else this Force Power fails automatically. You can spend a Force Point to impose a -10 penalty to the target's Grapple checks made to escape the Plant Surge. You can maintain Plant Surge from round to round, extending the normal duration. Maintaining the Plant Surge Force Power is a Swift Action, and you must make a new Use the Force check each round.","descriptor":["Control"],"dcChart":[{"dc":15,"effect":"Speed reduced to 0","description":"Target's Speed is reduced to 0 until the start of your next turn."}],"maintainable":true,"sourcebook":"Jedi Academy Training Manual","page":null,"tags":["force_power","control","terrain","area","standard_action","nature"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fp_prescience","name":"Prescience","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/aura.svg","system":{"powerLevel":1,"discipline":"telepathic","useTheForce":15,"time":"Swift Action","range":"Line of sight","target":"One target","duration":"Until end of next turn","effect":"The Force grants you a flash of insight in dealing with your enemies.","special":"You can spend a Force Point when you activate this Force Power to affect one additional target in your line of sight.","descriptor":["Mind-Affecting"],"dcChart":[{"dc":15,"effect":"+1 insight bonus","description":"You gain a +1 insight bonus to all Defenses and attack rolls against the target."},{"dc":20,"effect":"+2 insight bonus","description":"You gain a +2 insight bonus to all Defenses and attack rolls against the target."},{"dc":25,"effect":"+3 insight bonus","description":"You gain a +3 insight bonus to all Defenses and attack rolls against the target."}],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Legacy Era Campaign Guide","page":null,"tags":["force_power","awareness","defense","initiative","self_buff","swift_action"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fp_rend","name":"Rend","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","system":{"powerLevel":3,"discipline":"dark","useTheForce":15,"time":"Standard Action","range":"6 squares","target":"One target","duration":"Instantaneous","effect":"You can move a single target, whether it is a creature or object, in two different directions simultaneously.","special":"If your Use the Force check succeeds, you can spend a Force Point to deal an additional 2d6 points of damage to the target.","descriptor":["Dark Side"],"dcChart":[{"dc":15,"effect":"3d6 damage","description":"Target takes 3d6 points of damage."}],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Clone Wars Campaign Guide","page":null,"tags":["force_power","offense_force","telekinetic","single_target","damage","standard_action","armor_break"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fp_repulse","name":"Repulse","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","system":{"powerLevel":3,"discipline":"telekinetic","useTheForce":20,"time":"Standard Action","range":"Adjacent","target":"All adjacent targets","duration":"Instantaneous","effect":"You use The Force to clear an area around yourself.","special":"You can spend a Force Point to apply a -5 penalty to the target's Strength check to resist your Repulse. Additionally, after spending a Force Point, if you successfully push the target into a larger object, you deal an extra 2d6 points of damage from the extreme force of the pulse.","descriptor":["Telekinetic"],"dcChart":[{"dc":20,"effect":"Push 1+ squares","description":"Push target back 1 square plus 1 additional square for every 5 points by which you exceeded the target's Strength check."}],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Force Unleashed Campaign Guide","page":null,"tags":["force_power","offense_force","area","telekinetic","push","standard_action","battlefield_control"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fp_resistforce","name":"Resist Force","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/shield.svg","system":{"powerLevel":1,"discipline":"control","useTheForce":15,"time":"Standard Action","range":"Self","target":"Self","duration":"Until beginning of next turn","effect":"You use The Force to protect yourself from an opponent's Force Powers.","special":"You can spend a Force Point to apply the bonus provided by this Force Power to any two Defense scores of your choice. You can maintain Resist Force from round to round, extending the normal duration. Maintaining the Resist Force Force Power is a Swift Action. If you take damage while maintaining Resist Force, you must succeed on a Use the Force check (DC = 15 + damage taken) to continue maintaining the Resist Force.","descriptor":["Control"],"dcChart":[{"dc":15,"effect":"+1 Defense","description":"You gain +1 to one Defense score of your choice against Force Powers."},{"dc":20,"effect":"+2 Defense","description":"You gain +2 to one Defense score of your choice against Force Powers."},{"dc":25,"effect":"+3 Defense","description":"You gain +3 to one Defense score of your choice against Force Powers."}],"maintainable":true,"sourcebook":"Knights of the Old Republic Campaign Guide","page":null,"tags":["force_power","defense","anti_force","reaction","utf_defense","survivability"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fp_shatterpoint","name":"Shatterpoint","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","system":{"powerLevel":4,"discipline":"control","useTheForce":25,"time":"Swift Action","range":"Self","target":"Self","duration":"Until end of encounter","effect":"You can see the critical point of something, whether it is a person or object, that would shatter if struck at the right time.","special":"You can spend a Force Point to ignore the target's Damage Reduction in addition to gaining the normal effects of Shatterpoint.","descriptor":["Control"],"dcChart":[{"dc":25,"effect":"DT -5","description":"If your next attack hits, treat the target's Damage Threshold as 5 points lower than normal."},{"dc":30,"effect":"DT -10","description":"If your next attack hits, treat the target's Damage Threshold as 10 points lower than normal."},{"dc":35,"effect":"DT -15","description":"If your next attack hits, treat the target's Damage Threshold as 15 points lower than normal."},{"dc":40,"effect":"DT -20","description":"If your next attack hits, treat the target's Damage Threshold as 20 points lower than normal."}],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Clone Wars Campaign Guide","page":null,"tags":["force_power","offense_melee","offense_ranged","critical_setup","swift_action","damage_spike"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fp_slow","name":"Slow","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/slowdown.svg","system":{"powerLevel":2,"discipline":"telekinetic","useTheForce":15,"time":"Standard Action","range":"12 squares","target":"One creature or Droid","duration":"Until beginning of next turn","effect":"The Force enables you to slow your targets as if they are encumbered by an extremely heavy load, making it difficult for them to move.","special":"You can spend a Force Point to impose a -5 penalty to your target's Fortitude Defense against the use of this Force Power.","descriptor":["Telekinetic"],"dcChart":[{"dc":15,"effect":"Speed -1, Encumbered","description":"Target's Speed is reduced by 1 square until the beginning of your next turn."},{"dc":20,"effect":"Speed -2, Encumbered","description":"Target's Speed is reduced by 2 squares until the beginning of your next turn."},{"dc":25,"effect":"Speed -3, Encumbered","description":"Target's Speed is reduced by 3 squares until the beginning of your next turn."},{"dc":30,"effect":"Speed -4, Encumbered","description":"Target's Speed is reduced by 4 squares until the beginning of your next turn."}],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Knights of the Old Republic Campaign Guide","page":null,"tags":["force_power","control","debuff","single_target","speed_reduction","standard_action"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fp_stagger","name":"Stagger","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","system":{"powerLevel":2,"discipline":"telekinetic","useTheForce":15,"time":"Swift Action","range":"Adjacent","target":"One target adjacent to you","duration":"Instantaneous","effect":"You use The Force to lash out at a nearby enemy, causing it to stumble.","special":"You can spend a Force Point when you activate this Force Power to affect all enemies adjacent to you, in which case compare your Use the Force check result to each target's Fortitude Defense.","descriptor":["Telekinetic"],"dcChart":[{"dc":15,"effect":"2d6 damage, push 1","description":"Target takes 2d6 Force damage and is pushed 1 square away from you."}],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Legacy Era Campaign Guide","page":null,"tags":["force_power","control","debuff","single_target","action_denial","standard_action"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fp_technometry","name":"Technometry","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/computer.svg","system":{"powerLevel":2,"discipline":"telepathic","useTheForce":20,"time":"Standard Action","range":"Touch","target":"One Droid or device","duration":"Instantaneous","effect":"You can tap into and read technological devices and, in some cases, control them.","special":"You can spend a Force Point to learn two more pieces of information or extend one of the Droid-specific effects of this Force Power by one additional round.","descriptor":["Telepathic"],"dcChart":[{"dc":20,"effect":"Read device","description":"You discover one piece of information contained within the target's memory."},{"dc":25,"effect":"Control Droid","description":"You can jam the Droid's senses, deny Dexterity bonus, or force it to flee at top speed."}],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Clone Wars Campaign Guide","page":null,"tags":["force_power","tech","droid","device_control","utility","standard_action","skill_use_computer"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fp_thoughtbomb","name":"Thought Bomb","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","system":{"powerLevel":3,"discipline":"telepathic","useTheForce":20,"time":"Standard Action","range":"2 squares","target":"All opponents within 2 squares","duration":"Instantaneous","effect":"You use The Force to radiate out harmful waves of telepathy, damaging the minds of nearby foes.","special":"You can spend a Force Point to increase the damage dealt by this Force Power by an additional +2d6 points of Force damage.","descriptor":["Mind-Affecting"],"dcChart":[{"dc":20,"effect":"2d6 damage, -Swift","description":"Target takes 2d6 Force damage and loses its Swift Action on its next turn."}],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Jedi Academy Training Manual","page":null,"tags":["force_power","offense_force","area","dark_side","mind_affecting","standard_action","burst"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fp_valor","name":"Valor","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/shield.svg","system":{"powerLevel":2,"discipline":"light","useTheForce":15,"time":"Standard Action","range":"12 squares","target":"One ally","duration":"Until beginning of next turn","effect":"You call upon the strength of The Force, reaching out to your ally and sharing your strength with them.","special":"You can spend a Force Point when you activate this Force Power to have the bonus apply against all effects that target Will Defense (not just Mind-Affecting and Fear effects). You can maintain Valor from round to round, extending the normal duration. Maintaining the Valor Force Power is a Swift Action. If you take damage while maintaining Valor, you must succeed on a Use the Force check (DC = 15 + damage taken) to continue maintaining the Valor.","descriptor":["Light Side"],"dcChart":[{"dc":15,"effect":"+1 Will Defense","description":"The target gains a +1 bonus to their Will Defense against Mind-Affecting and Fear effects."},{"dc":20,"effect":"+2 Will Defense","description":"The target gains a +2 bonus to their Will Defense against Mind-Affecting and Fear effects."},{"dc":25,"effect":"+5 Will Defense","description":"The target gains a +5 bonus to their Will Defense against Mind-Affecting and Fear effects."},{"dc":30,"effect":"+10 Will Defense","description":"The target gains a +10 bonus to their Will Defense against Mind-Affecting and Fear effects."}],"maintainable":true,"sourcebook":"Knights of the Old Republic Campaign Guide","page":null,"tags":["force_power","ally_support","team_buff","morale","defense","standard_action"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fp_wound","name":"Wound","type":"force-power","img":"icons/svg/skull.svg","system":{"powerLevel":2,"discipline":"dark","useTheForce":15,"time":"Standard Action","range":"6 squares","target":"One creature","duration":"Instantaneous","effect":"You cause spasms in the lungs of your targets, painfully injuring them.","special":"You can spend a Force Point to increase the damage dealt by an additional +2d6 points of Force damage. If the target moves 1 or more steps down the Condition Track as a result of being damaged by this Force Power, the Condition becomes Persistent until the target is treated with a DC 20 Treat Injury check to perform Surgery.","descriptor":["Dark Side"],"dcChart":[{"dc":15,"effect":"4d6 damage","description":"Target receives 4d6 points of Force damage."}],"maintainable":false,"sourcebook":"Knights of the Old Republic Campaign Guide","page":null,"tags":["force_power","offense_force","damage","single_target","dark_side","standard_action"],"inSuite":false,"uses":{"current":0,"max":0},"costNumeric":null,"executionModel":"FORCE_POWER"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
